{"tid":673824,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[遵理]有冇人報左Hong Sir Mock 卷 覺得中左伏？","createTime":"2018-05-22T07:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T08:12:09.000Z","uid":81926,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a65cdfc1bb7db9308ce169cf38177e5d17d7dd4a","tid":673824,"uid":81926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"我報左Hong sir 4月個終極模疑試<br />\n屌你老母 成630蚊 仲貴撚過報DSE<br />\n算 為左成績我忍<br />\n<br />\n之但係我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一心諗住咁撚貴一個mock, 應該有人改卷啦, 仆佢個街竟然係播片對答案<br />\n好當我on9 冇問清楚 (佢都冇寫明）<br />\n<br />\n但我頂你個肺呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲答全撚部 係全撚部都係point form呀, 係後面加幾句呀媽係女人就當係答案, 一篇範文都冇<br />\n技巧呀 拆字呀 乜撚都冇講<br />\n做就做左5粒幾鐘<br />\n講答案就講得果一陣<br />\n<br />\n好啦 當630 買tips啦<br />\n宜家考完喇<br />\n竟然一條分題都唔中 連題型都唔中<br />\n屌你大拿拿成630 我拎去課金抽空氣唔好？<br />\n<br />\n有冇報左hong sir mock 既話我聽邊忽係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0d03b9ae170732cfe63b43480363a7763bdcd7","tid":673824,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"依家ｍｏｃｋ都咁貴<br />\n<br />\n我１０年前　補習<br />\n<br />\n果堆ｍｏｃｋ卷　部份人係送　<br />\n或者報開果堆平平地　１００，２００蚊　比你玩埋"},{"pid":"69b08a73baa783d8b1dc86d7c1ce24ff489097e3","tid":673824,"uid":81926,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:36:44.000Z","msg":"比最過份果幾頁大家睇下<br />\n啲答案仲短過佢條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[member<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/153547_de1dda90b5dcb00222ee66a8f789a996.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F153547_de1dda90b5dcb00222ee66a8f789a996.png&h=8c012a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/